'''Ōzono Kofun''' (大園古墳) was a {{ill|Scallop Kofun|ja|帆立貝形古墳|1=Scallop Kofun|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=draft}} located in {{ill|Takaishi, Osaka|ja|高石市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Osaka Prefecture|ja|大阪府|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=draft}}, Japan. The mound is no longer extant.

== Overview ==
<div class="thumb tright">
{| class="wikitable" style="background:#ffffff;text-align:center;font-size:85%;"
